  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1701855108\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Checkmaze is a simple game that's based on actual chess scenarios and uses original chess pieces. With more than 50 levels of puzzles that rely exclusively on classical chess pieces, there's plenty to keep you challenged, especially if you're a fan of classic old chess.<br><br>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/61a33b15ce774f3830e236c318024bf7.poster.avif?t=1701855108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/61a33b15ce774f3830e236c318024bf7.webm?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/61a33b15ce774f3830e236c318024bf7.mp4?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But that's not all Checkmaze has to offer. Checkmaze  becomes even more complex, surprising, and enjoyable as new pieces are added.  We have new pieces like traps, portals, and wizards with different abilities and behaviors that add an exciting twist to the game.<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/a39d5d773b5a9797a78c70b407224098.poster.avif?t=1701855108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/a39d5d773b5a9797a78c70b407224098.webm?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/a39d5d773b5a9797a78c70b407224098.mp4?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>New pieces  and mechanics are being added. <br>3 new chess pieces and minimum 18 level for each of them.<br>4 great levels.<br>Moving pieces were added. Now mazes are changing as you play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/b0d68d666690a585b22bb52ad3942f9b.poster.avif?t=1701855108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/b0d68d666690a585b22bb52ad3942f9b.webm?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/b0d68d666690a585b22bb52ad3942f9b.mp4?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>#### How to Play #### <br>- you control the white pieces in CheckMaze.<br>- your only purpose is to reach to the king and check it.<br><br>check the puzzle below and see how many moves it takes to reach checking position<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/a759a0d3374f879c9985a46353d7cf9a.avif?t=1701855108\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1701855108\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Checkmaze is a simple game that's based on actual chess scenarios and uses original chess pieces. With more than 50 levels of puzzles that rely exclusively on classical chess pieces, there's plenty to keep you challenged, especially if you're a fan of classic old chess.<br><br>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/61a33b15ce774f3830e236c318024bf7.poster.avif?t=1701855108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/61a33b15ce774f3830e236c318024bf7.webm?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/61a33b15ce774f3830e236c318024bf7.mp4?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But that's not all Checkmaze has to offer. Checkmaze  becomes even more complex, surprising, and enjoyable as new pieces are added.  We have new pieces like traps, portals, and wizards with different abilities and behaviors that add an exciting twist to the game.<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/a39d5d773b5a9797a78c70b407224098.poster.avif?t=1701855108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/a39d5d773b5a9797a78c70b407224098.webm?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/a39d5d773b5a9797a78c70b407224098.mp4?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>New pieces  and mechanics are being added. <br>3 new chess pieces and minimum 18 level for each of them.<br>4 great levels.<br>Moving pieces were added. Now mazes are changing as you play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/b0d68d666690a585b22bb52ad3942f9b.poster.avif?t=1701855108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/b0d68d666690a585b22bb52ad3942f9b.webm?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/b0d68d666690a585b22bb52ad3942f9b.mp4?t=1701855108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>#### How to Play #### <br>- you control the white pieces in CheckMaze.<br>- your only purpose is to reach to the king and check it.<br><br>check the puzzle below and see how many moves it takes to reach checking position<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348970/extras/a759a0d3374f879c9985a46353d7cf9a.avif?t=1701855108\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
